WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:01.435 --> 00:00:02.936
BUT CAN'T AFFORD
THE LEGAL EXPENSES?

00:00:02.970 --> 00:00:04.905 line:0%
 
- HI, I'M RON FUNCHES.

00:00:04.938 --> 00:00:07.274 line:0%
 
JUST TO BE CLEAR,
I AM A PUBLIC DEFENDER.

00:00:07.307 --> 00:00:09.676 line:0%
 
I KNOW WHAT YOU'RE SAYING.
"WHY DOES A PUBLIC DEFENDER

00:00:09.710 --> 00:00:13.881 line:0%
 
NEED A COMMERCIAL?"

00:00:13.914 --> 00:00:16.383 line:0%
 
THE BAD NEWS IS
YOU'RE GOING TO BE CONVICTED.

00:00:16.416 --> 00:00:18.385 line:0%
 
- GUILTY!
- WE TRIED.

00:00:18.418 --> 00:00:20.721 line:0%
 
AND IF I'M RANDOMLY SELECTED
TO BE YOUR LAWYER,

00:00:20.754 --> 00:00:23.357 line:0%
 
I'LL BRING YOU A NICE BOX
OF MY AUNT SANDI'S

00:00:23.390 --> 00:00:25.759 line:0%
 
PECAN SANDIES.

00:00:25.792 --> 00:00:27.227 line:0%
 
[cell phone rings]

00:00:27.261 --> 00:00:29.029 line:0%
 
GUESS MY WORK'S NEVER DONE.

00:00:29.062 --> 00:00:30.697 line:0%
 
I HAVE TO GO MEET
WITH A NEW CLIENT.

00:00:30.731 --> 00:00:32.566 line:0%
 
OR SHOULD I SAY FRIEND?

00:00:32.599 --> 00:00:35.002
- MY WIFE IS DEAD.
I'VE LOST ALL MY MONEY.

00:00:35.035 --> 00:00:37.337
I CAN NO LONGER AFFORD
MY HIGH-POWERED ATTORNEY,

00:00:37.371 --> 00:00:40.107
AND EVERYONE'S ABANDONED ME--
THAT'S WHY I'M HERE.

00:00:40.140 --> 00:00:42.776
- PECAN SANDIE?

00:00:42.809 --> 00:00:44.945
- I'M MORE OF A MINT
MILANO MAN MYSELF, BUT--

00:00:44.978 --> 00:00:46.146
- SO YOU KILLED YOUR WIFE?

00:00:46.180 --> 00:00:47.881
- I NEVER LAID A HAND
ON MY WIFE,

00:00:47.915 --> 00:00:50.350
EXCEPT ON OCCASIONAL
SPECIAL EVENINGS.

00:00:50.384 --> 00:00:53.453
- [laughs]
- [chuckles weakly]

00:00:53.487 --> 00:00:54.588
IT FEELS REALLY GOOD
TO LAUGH.

00:00:54.621 --> 00:00:55.956
- YOU LOOK LIKE A HIGHLIGHTER.

00:00:55.989 --> 00:00:58.091
- AND YOU LOOK LIKE A HAIRY
CHOCOLATE GUMMI BEAR.

00:00:58.125 --> 00:00:59.560
- [laughs]

00:00:59.593 --> 00:01:01.428
- I GOTTA TELL YOU,
MR. FUNCHES,

00:01:01.461 --> 00:01:04.765
WE'RE GONNA LAUGH ALL THE WAY
TO NOT GOING TO JAIL.

00:01:04.798 --> 00:01:08.502
- EVEN THOUGH YOU'RE NOT GUILTY,
I'M GONNA TAKE THE CASE.

00:01:08.535 --> 00:01:10.337
- DO YOU HAVE A CHOICE IN THAT?
- NO.

00:01:10.370 --> 00:01:11.505
- 'CAUSE YOU'RE A PUBLIC
DEFENDER.

00:01:11.538 --> 00:01:13.807
- YEAH.

00:01:13.841 --> 00:01:15.342
- DR. ARMOND, PLEASE RISE.

00:01:15.375 --> 00:01:18.879
YOU STAND HERE ACCUSED
OF MURDER IN THE SECOND DEGREE.

00:01:18.912 --> 00:01:20.180
HOW DO YOU PLEAD?

00:01:20.214 --> 00:01:23.083 line:0%
 
- GUILTY...
OF LOVING MY WIFE.

00:01:23.116 --> 00:01:24.218 line:0%
 
- [laughs]

00:01:24.251 --> 00:01:27.421 line:0%
 
[upbeat wrap-up music]

